data.description: Amazing and unique owner-occupy or investment opportunity located in the Island neighborhood of Logan! Fantastic location, near Utah State University, shopping centers and downtown amenities. Very well taken care and maintained legal duplex and single family home; for a total of three units on same parcel ID. This 0.39 acre property also includes a large workshop w/ garage, boasting over 2,000 square feet of space with electrical and gas connected; two storage sheds; fully landscaped, maintained yard with mature trees; two long driveways provide extra parking space. Fantastic tenants and full occupancy history, separate meter connections, and impressive rental income make this property turnkey! Agent related to seller.
